export const AUTH_FORM_SUCCESS = "AUTH_FORM_SUCCESS"; // this action will pop up when we login or register correctly
export const AUTH_FORM_FAIL = "AUTH_FORM_FAIL"; // this will pop up when a form will fail eg enter wrong email etc
export const AUTH_ERROR = "AUTH_ERROR"; // pops up when token expires etc
export const USER_IS_LOADED = "USER_IS_LOADED"; // pops up when user logs in
export const LOG_OUT = "LOG_OUT"; //pops up when user logs out
